# VTSuperResolutionScalerConfiguration.Revision

**Enumeration**

Available algorithm revisions.

## Declaration

```swift
enum Revision
```

## Overview

A new enum case with a higher revision number is added when the processing algorithm is updated. The [doc://com.apple.videotoolbox/documentation/VideoToolbox/VTSuperResolutionScalerConfiguration/defaultRevision] property provides the default algorithm revision.
